('Marketing', 'mid', 'The Brand vs Performance', 'Leadership wants to cut brand spend entirely to fund performance marketing for faster ROI. You believe brand is essential for long-term. What do you do?', '[{"id":"A","label":"Make the case for brand with data on long-term customer acquisition costs","why_it_matters":"Shows evidence-based advocacy","signals":["data-driven advocacy","long-term thinking"]},{"id":"B","label":"Propose a hybrid model that protects brand minimally while boosting performance","why_it_matters":"Shows pragmatic compromise","signals":["balanced approach","stakeholder management"]},{"id":"C","label":"Agree to the shift for one quarter as a test, track leading indicators closely","why_it_matters":"Shows experimental openness","signals":["test-and-learn","flexibility"]}]', '["cognitive_patterns", "communication_style"]', 'Each approach has merit in different contexts.'),
('Marketing', 'senior', 'The Viral Moment', 'Your brand unexpectedly went viral for something unrelated to your core message. Do you capitalize on it or refocus on strategy?', '[{"id":"A","label":"Ride the wave—viral moments are rare, maximize exposure","why_it_matters":"Shows opportunistic marketing","signals":["agility","opportunity capture"]},{"id":"B","label":"Gently redirect attention back to core brand message while it is hot","why_it_matters":"Shows strategic opportunism","signals":["brand discipline","strategic pivot"]},{"id":"C","label":"Observe and learn—document what resonated for future campaigns","why_it_matters":"Shows learning orientation","signals":["analytical mindset","pattern recognition"]}]', '["execution_style", "cognitive_patterns"]', 'All responses show marketing judgment.'),
('Marketing', 'lead', 'The Agency Fail', 'Your creative agency delivered work that does not meet the brief. Launch is in 10 days. What do you do?', '[{"id":"A","label":"Have a direct conversation, demand rework on expedited timeline","why_it_matters":"Shows assertive vendor management","signals":["vendor accountability","urgency communication"]},{"id":"B","label":"Bring work in-house for this launch, reevaluate agency relationship after","why_it_matters":"Shows pragmatic problem-solving","signals":["resourcefulness","contingency planning"]},{"id":"C","label":"Delay launch to get it right—quality over speed","why_it_matters":"Shows quality commitment","signals":["quality standards","timeline flexibility"]}]', '["execution_style", "problem_solving_vectors"]', 'Each approach demonstrates leadership thinking.'),

