('Operations', 'mid', 'The Process vs Speed', 'A new hire is bypassing the approval process to ship things faster. Their work is good but it sets a bad precedent. What do you do?', '[{"id":"A","label":"Address it directly—process exists for good reasons, enforce compliance","why_it_matters":"Shows process discipline","signals":["process adherence","precedent awareness"]},{"id":"B","label":"Investigate if the process is too slow—maybe it needs improvement","why_it_matters":"Shows systems thinking","signals":["process improvement mindset","root cause analysis"]},{"id":"C","label":"Have a coaching conversation about when and why process matters","why_it_matters":"Shows developmental approach","signals":["coaching mindset","educational approach"]}]', '["execution_style", "communication_style"]', 'All choices show operational judgment.'),
('Operations', 'senior', 'The Vendor Crisis', 'Your key vendor just raised prices 30% mid-contract claiming market conditions. Operations depend on them. What do you do?', '[{"id":"A","label":"Push back hard—contract is contract, escalate to legal if needed","why_it_matters":"Shows contract enforcement","signals":["contractual discipline","negotiation strength"]},{"id":"B","label":"Negotiate a phased increase while sourcing alternatives","why_it_matters":"Shows pragmatic negotiation","signals":["vendor management","transition planning"]},{"id":"C","label":"Accept the increase for now, accelerate migration to alternative vendors","why_it_matters":"Shows strategic adaptation","signals":["strategic flexibility","long-term planning"]}]', '["problem_solving_vectors", "execution_style"]', 'Each approach is valid depending on leverage and alternatives.'),
('Operations', 'lead', 'The Scale Challenge', 'The company is growing 3x and your current processes will not scale. You have limited budget for new tools. What do you do?', '[{"id":"A","label":"Hire ahead of the curve—invest in people who can build new processes","why_it_matters":"Shows people investment","signals":["talent-first","capability building"]},{"id":"B","label":"Automate what you can with low-cost tools, accept some manual work temporarily","why_it_matters":"Shows pragmatic scaling","signals":["scrappy mindset","phased automation"]},{"id":"C","label":"Work with leadership to get budget—this is a strategic investment","why_it_matters":"Shows advocacy for resources","signals":["resource advocacy","strategic framing"]}]', '["cognitive_patterns", "execution_style"]', 'All approaches show operational leadership.'),

